title: Thales Payshield 10K Health Diag Self Test
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/Payshield
license: Proprietary
distribution: Proprietary
description:
 This check monitors the Health Diag self test of a Thales Payshield HSM via SNMP. It reports the result of the self test and provides the full self test result string, including the status of cryptographic and hardware components.

 The check interprets the SNMP value as follows:
 - 0 = Health Test Critical (CRITICAL)
 - 1 = Health Test OK (OK)
 - 3 = Health Test Unknown (UNKNOWN)

inventory:
 This check does not create inventory entries.


 Prerequisite: The Health Test count collection must be enabled on the HSM. See Payshield console command HEALTHENABLE for more details.
